Package: llmshieldr
Title: A Pharma-First LLM Security Layer for R
Description: Wraps any R LLM call with preflight prompt scanning, automated
    redaction, policy enforcement, postflight output checks, and audit records.
    Built for regulated industries including pharma, finance, and legal.
